          <text>
                    <body>
                              <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Marysville California</placeName>
                                        <date>January 8<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 1853</date>.</p>
                              <p>
                                        <addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(3)">Dear sir this <sic>informes</sic> you<lb/> of the
                                        Good health of min. and Prosperity in General of our Bro.<lb/>
                                        <sic>Israelits</sic> in this State. <placeName>San
                                                  Francisco</placeName> is advancing<lb/> very much
                                        in this cause of <sic>Religius</sic> Points. I have seen
                                        an<lb/> Advertisement in on paper the other day the want of
                                        a Reader<lb/> Schamis &amp; Schochet,.
                                                  <placeName>Sacramento</placeName> also, in
                                                  <placeName>Sacramento</placeName><lb/> was a Great
                                        fire this winter and all around the <sic>Sinagoge</sic><lb/>
                                        the Houses Burnt and the <sic>Sinagoge</sic> and the
                                                  <add>Hebrew</add>
                                        <add>?</add><lb/> Sefty <sic>witout</sic> injury. Hebrew
                                        Benevolent <sic>Societys</sic> are<lb/> forming in both
                                        those <sic>Citys</sic>. and are very
                                        <sic>Prosperus</sic>!</p>
                              <p>P. S. in this country there is nothing <sic>wanding</sic> but 1 or
                                        2 very smart<lb/> and through going man to take interest in
                                        the cause of Jewish<lb/> Religion, and then all will
                                                  <sic>gow</sic> Right.</p>
                              <p>I have just found in one of my friends Houses <sic>on</sic> of your<lb/>
                                        <sic>Litle</sic> Books calld the <sic>Accitint</sic> and
                                        Like it very much, but<lb/> I could not ascertain what the
                                        Price of it was for he is not<lb/> a subscriber he brought
                                        it with him from <placeName>New Orleans</placeName>. I
                                                  <sic>therfor</sic> take the Liberty of writing to
                                        you for information of the Price<lb/> if you will write me.
                                        I will Cheerfully send you the Amount<lb/> and try to get
                                        subscribers to the same, if you will Place as much<lb/>
                                        confidence in me as one of the flock you may send me a
                                        copy<lb/> to <sic>Acompany</sic> the Letter and by first
                                        mail the stating price<lb/> will be at your hand as soon as
                                        it can reach <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName><lb/> and if
                                        you have <sic>anny</sic> old <sic>once</sic> I wish you
                                        would send me<lb/> some, and Charge me
                                        <sic>Acordingly</sic>, by doing so you will oblige<lb/> your
                                        most Sincere friend</p>
                              <p rend="indent(8)"><persName role="author">E. M.
                                        Mayer</persName>.</p>
                              <p>I expect an answer as soon as you receive my Letter<lb/>
                                        <sic>Exept</sic> my Respect and Good Wishes from your
                                        friend</p>
                    </body>
